snippet.title: PARANOIHELL - Trailer (2D Survival Horror Game)
snippet.description:
Available now on Itch and Steam

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/11...
Itch.io: https://lum-scum.itch.io/paranoihell

PARANOIHELL is chaotic nightmare about a woman trying to get home. Run, hide, fight back... whatever you choose, will you make it home alive?
